    "en": {
      "title": "18-hr water cut for the weekend",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st); The National Water Supply and Drainage Board (NWSDB) said the water supply will be interrupted for 18 hours during the weekend for multiple areas.",
        "The water cut will be in effect from 8.00 am on Saturday (3) to 2.00 am on Sunday (4) in Colombo, Dehiwela \u2013 Mt. Lavinia, Kotte, and Kaduwela M.C areas, Maharagama, Boralasgamuwa, Kolonnawa U. C. areas, Kotikawatta Mulleriyawa P. S. areas, Rathmalana and Katubedda.",
        "Suspect arrested after failed assassination attempt on Argentine vice president"
      ],
